cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI

The paper deals with the construction and investigation of a novel type of neural network for pattern classification problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the use of regularized weights direct determination to improve the generalization ability of the network, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with the comparison of the proposed method with other classification algorithms, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses the computational scalability and efficiency of the proposed method, which could fall under cs.SI (Systems and Control).
